'''二苯基氯化膦'''是一种[[有机磷化合物|有机磷化合物]]，化学式为(C<sub>6</sub>H<sub>5</sub>)<sub>2</sub>PCl，可简写为Ph<sub>2</sub>PCl。它是无色油状液体，具有大蒜气味，ppb级别的浓度即可被检测到。它容易和很多[[亲核试剂|亲核试剂]]（如水）反应，并易被空气氧化。它在有机合成中用于引入Ph<sub>2</sub>P基团。<ref name=Quin>Quin, L. D. ''A Guide to Organophosphorus Chemistry''; Wiley IEEE: New York, 2000; pp 44-69. {{ISBN|0-471-31824-8}}</ref>

== 合成 ==
二苯基氯化膦在工业上可由[[苯|苯]]和[[三氯化磷|三氯化磷]]反应得到。反应在600 °C的高温发生，先生成[[苯基二氯化膦|苯基二氯化膦]]和[[氯化氢|HCl]]，然后二氯化物在气相经重分配反应得到二苯基氯化膦。<ref name=Quin/><ref name=Svara/>
:2 PhPCl<sub>2</sub> → Ph<sub>2</sub>PCl + PCl<sub>3</sub>
以[[三苯基膦|三苯基膦]]和[[三氯化磷|三氯化磷]]的反应也能得到产物：
:PCl<sub>3</sub> +  2 PPh<sub>3</sub> → 2 Ph<sub>2</sub>PCl

{{le|二苯基氧化膦|Diphenylphosphine oxide}}和[[乙酰氯|乙酰氯]]在[[四氢呋喃|四氢呋喃]]中反应，也能得到二苯基氯化膦。<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Zhang|first1=Jian-Qiu|last2=Yang|first2=Shangdong|last3=Han|first3=Li-Biao|title=Facial conversion of secondary phosphine oxides R1R2P(O)H to chlorophosphines R1R2PCl by acetyl chloride|journal=Tetrahedron Letters|volume=61|issue=10|year=2020|pages=151556|issn=00404039|doi=10.1016/j.tetlet.2019.151556}}</ref>

== 反应 ==
二苯基氯化膦遇水分解。它可以被[[过氧化氢|过氧化氢]]氧化，生成[[:d:Q27117287|二苯基膦酸]]。<ref name=Horner />它可以被[[五氟氯化硫|五氟氯化硫]]氧化，得到二苯基三氟化磷；<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Fraser|first1=C.J.W.|last2=McCartney|first2=M.E.|last3=Sharp|first3=D.W.A.|last4=Winfield|first4=J.M.|title=Oxidative fluorination of substituted phosphines with sulphur chloride pentafluoride|journal=Journal of Inorganic and Nuclear Chemistry|volume=34|issue=4|year=1972|pages=1455–1456|issn=00221902|doi=10.1016/0022-1902(72)80347-6}}</ref>它被[[氯|氯]]氧化得到二苯基三氯化磷：<ref>Bermann, Manfred; Van Wazer, John R. μ-​Nitride-​bis[amidodiphenylphosphorus]​(1+) chloride. ''Inorganic Syntheses', 1974. 15: 199-202. ISSN: 0073-8077.</ref>
: Ph<sub>2</sub>PCl  +  Cl<sub>2</sub>  →  Ph<sub>2</sub>PCl<sub>3</sub>
它和[[甲醇|甲醇]]反应，生成二苯基甲氧基膦。<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Błocka|first1=Aleksandra|last2=Woźnicki|first2=Paweł|last3=Stankevič|first3=Marek|last4=Chaładaj|first4=Wojciech|title=Pd-catalyzed intramolecular addition of active methylene compounds to alkynes with subsequent cross-coupling with (hetero)aryl halides|journal=RSC Advances|volume=9|issue=68|year=2019|pages=40152–40167|issn=2046-2069|doi=10.1039/C9RA08002C}}</ref>它和2-乙炔基吡啶在[[三乙胺|三乙胺]]存在下、[[碘化亚铜|碘化亚铜]]催化下于[[甲苯|甲苯]]中加热反应，得到2-吡啶基乙炔基二苯基膦。<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Guo|first1=Jiami|last2=Mao|first2=Chenlu|last3=Deng|first3=Bin|last4=Ye|first4=Liyi|last5=Yin|first5=Yingwu|last6=Gao|first6=Yuxing|last7=Tu|first7=Song|title=Azobisisobutyronitrile-Initiated Oxidative C–H Functionalization of Simple Alcohols with Diaryl(arylethynyl)phosphine Oxides: A Metal-Free Approach toward Hydroxymethyl Benzo[b]phosphole Oxides and 6H-Indeno[2,1-b]phosphindole 5-Oxide Derivatives|journal=The Journal of Organic Chemistry|volume=85|issue=10|year=2020|pages=6359–6371|issn=0022-3263|doi=10.1021/acs.joc.0c00118}}</ref>

== 用途 ==
二苯基氯化膦可用于合成其它[[膦|膦]]类化合物，一种方法是使用[[格氏试剂|格氏试剂]]：<ref name=Svara>Svara, J.; Weferling, N.; Hofmann, T. "Phosphorus Compounds, Organic," In 'Ullmann's Encyclopedia of Industrial Chemistry, 7th ed.; Wiley-VCH: 2008; {{DOI|10.1002/14356007.a19_545.pub2}}; Accessed: February 18, 2008.</ref>
:Ph<sub>2</sub>PCl + MgRX   →    Ph<sub>2</sub>PR  +  MgClX

反应中生成的膦可进一步用于杀虫剂（如{{le|苯硫磷|EPN (insecticide)}}）、塑料稳定剂（Sandostab P-EPQ）、卤素化合物催化剂、阻燃剂（环膦酰羧酸酐）及紫外线硬化涂料体系（用于牙科材料）的合成，这使Ph<sub>2</sub>PCl成为重要的反应中间体。<ref name=Quin/><ref name=Svara/>

=== 二苯基膦基化合物前体 ===

二苯基氯化膦可用作二苯基膦基化合物合成的前体，它和金属[[钠|钠]]在[[1,4-二噁烷|1,4-二氧六环]]中回流反应，可以制得二苯基膦基钠。<ref>{{cite journal | doi = 10.1071/CH9850111 | last1 = Roy | first1 = Jackson W | last2 = Thomson | first2 = RJ | last3 = MacKay.m.f | first3 = . | title = The Stereochemistry of Organometallic Compounds. XXV. The Stereochemistry of Displacements of Secondary Methanesulfonate and ''p''-Toluene-sulfonate esters by Diphenylphosphide Ions. X-ray Crystal Structure of (5α-Cholestan-3α-yl)diphenylphosphine Oxide | journal = [[Australian_Journal_of_Chemistry|Australian Journal of Chemistry]] | year = 1985 | volume = 38 | issue = 1 | pages = 111–18}}</ref>
:Ph<sub>2</sub>PCl  +  2 Na   →   Ph<sub>2</sub>PNa  +  NaCl

它和过量的[[氢化铝锂|氢化铝锂]]反应，可以得到[[二苯基膦|二苯基膦]]。<ref>{{cite journal | doi = 10.1021/om9005615 | last1 = Stepanova | first1 = Valeria A. | last2 = Dunina | first2 = Valery V. | last3 = Smoliakova | first3 = Irina P. | title = Reactions of Cyclopalladated Complexes with Lithium Diphenylphosphide | journal = [[Organometallics|Organometallics]] | year = 2009 | volume = 28 | issue = 22 | pages = 6546–6558}}</ref>
:4 Ph<sub>2</sub>PCl  +  LiAlH<sub>4</sub>  →  4 Ph<sub>2</sub>PH  +  LiCl  +  AlCl<sub>3</sub>
以上两种二苯基膦化合物都可用于合成其它有机膦配体。<ref>Xu, Qihai; Kwon, Ohyun. 1,​2-​Bis(diphenylphosphino)​methane. ''e-EROS Encyclopedia of Reagents for Organic Synthesis''. pp 1-4. ISBN 978-0-470-84289-8.</ref><ref>{{cite journal|last1=Kissel|first1=Alexander A.|last2=Mahrova|first2=Tatyana V.|last3=Lyubov|first3=Dmitry M.|last4=Cherkasov|first4=Anton V.|last5=Fukin|first5=Georgy K.|last6=Trifonov|first6=Alexander A.|last7=Del Rosal|first7=Iker|last8=Maron|first8=Laurent|title=Metallacyclic yttrium alkyl and hydrido complexes: synthesis, structures and catalytic activity in intermolecular olefin hydrophosphination and hydroamination|journal=Dalton Transactions|volume=44|issue=27|year=2015|pages=12137–12148|issn=1477-9226|doi=10.1039/C5DT00129C}}</ref>

